c: 5
v: 60
t: "Iti (Muhammad (SAW) kuvanhu veGwaro): “Ndingakuudzei here pamusoro pechimwe chinhu chakaipa kudarika ichochi pamubairo kubva kuna Allah? Avo (maJudha) vakave vanorengerwa naAllah uye nekutsamwirwa, uye neavo (vamwe) vakasandurwa kuita tsoko nenguruve, uye neavo vainamata Twaaghoot (zvidhori kana kuti vanamwari venhema); vakadaro vachave munzvimbo yakashata (pazuva rekumutswa mumoto), uye vakanyanyorasika kubva munzira tsvene (muhupenyu hwepano pasi).”"